{"tid":452263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【凶兆？】英成群八爪魚爬上岸「等死」 當地人大惑不解","createTime":"2017-10-30T04:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T07:41:00.000Z","uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0ba680e74434902629cbd63903bf5445a6eb59","tid":452263,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:18:55.000Z","msg":"英國威爾斯一個海灘突然遭八爪魚「入侵」，成群八爪魚無故爬上岸，令當地人大惑不解。<br />\n<br />\n錫爾迪金（Ceredigion）一個海灘單是上周五晚已經有約20隻八爪魚爬上岸，但原來前一晚數量更多。在當地經營船公司的商家指，晚上10時左右發現八爪魚爬上岸，原因未明，「可能近日海浪較大，但我從未見過這個情況」。<br />\n<br />\n老闆指八爪魚不可以離開水源太久，呼籲遊客在岸上見到八爪魚的話，應將八爪魚送回海中，「今早已經有好幾隻死八爪魚決被沖上岸了」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171029/large/1509276269_d1e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171029%2Flarge%2F1509276269_d1e5.jpg&h=63309d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171029/large/1509276270_959d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171029%2Flarge%2F1509276270_959d.jpg&h=ce810788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171029/large/1509276271_84b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171029%2Flarge%2F1509276271_84b4.jpg&h=987a469e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171030/57391095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171030%2F57391095&d=smCtCamarhrpjCAdrbEdahOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b7950442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171030%2F57391095&h=5b41091c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171030/57391095</a>"},{"pid":"c4852b63a4512133bc6282baabcb2348b9413875","tid":452263,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"海底地震"},{"pid":"92d9fbd8fde23248448465e3bdce566b853e78e0","tid":452263,"uid":12458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"叫大陸狗過去清場啦"},{"pid":"efaca928c9fd73746ce3baa00177025fe58495a8","tid":452263,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:42:49.000Z","msg":"2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ed3ac5db54ffaa4a836ccd5bff1df34e1b33d3","tid":452263,"uid":2567,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"科斯的孤兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9d524166348e27ccab650a8c8bf23b27c24612","tid":452263,"uid":59567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"賭波輸左裸跑出事"},{"pid":"48a88e42289702c736ed5f871b1df5a86edb6446","tid":452263,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2017-5 =2012<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d36b17fb6bb0f6467e5b1fcd63bcca817c7143","tid":452263,"uid":139815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"肯定是支爆前的先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c09491754587a5aaca767c15d78d74bd44b4ec","tid":452263,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e977f956f79487b26b81131a882702995f5514","tid":452263,"u